Package org.example.view.gui.listener

Class Event

java.lang.Object
java.util.EventObject
org.example.view.gui.listener.Event
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Event extends EventObject
Custom event class that extends EventObject. It provides additional properties to handle application-specific events with optional data.
